      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "x": 40,
      "y": 64,
      "width": 1240,
      "height": 22,
      "text": "目的：呈现商品供给平台的核心业务对象、生命周期与发布治理关系；模型层次：逻辑模型 + 关键物理字段摘要；范围：Draft / Task / Staging / Review / Publish / Reliability。",
      "originalText": "目的：呈现商品供给平台的核心业务对象、生命周期与发布治理关系；模型层次：逻辑模型 + 关键物理字段摘要；范围：Draft / Task / Staging / Review / Publish / Reliability。",
      "fontSize": 14,
      "fontFamily": 8,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "middle",
      "strokeColor": "#64748b",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
